#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Atacked00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm not much good in a fight, so if I run\n"
"into a monster, my only options are to\n"
"run away or to hide."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Atacked01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Sources say there are still monsters\n"
"around.<2.pa> These sources are my own\n"
"eyes, so they're fairly reliable."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Failed00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I've never been strong enough to take on\n"
"monsters on my own, but maybe I'll start\n"
"training to protect myself."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Failed01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Just as the rumors say, the number of\n"
"monsters around here is on the rise.<2.pa>\n"
"Finally, I was able to verify some info."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (long)
msgctxt "Guardian00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I've heard all about <2.se_co>Guardians<3.re_co>.<4.pa> And\n"
"everything I've heard indicates we\n"
"should run for our lives!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: sound
#. 5: pause (short)
msgctxt "MSG_Kyu_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Now this is a juicy tidbit of info...<2.pa> What's\n"
"that? You wanna know the info too?\n"
"<3.so>Well, OK, but you didn't hear it from me.\n"
"<4.so>I heard that if you're trying to take down\n"
"a monster, a head shot with a bow from\n"
"a distance is pretty effective.\n"
"You already knew that?<5.pa> Well, I never said\n"
"it was a little-known rumor, now did I?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "MSG_Kyu_00_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You didn't hear it from me, but they say\n"
"that one of the best ways to take down a\n"
"monster is with a head shot from afar."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: pause (long)
#. 5: sound
msgctxt "MSG_Kyu_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>If you're only speaking with me because\n"
"you wanna stockpile information for\n"
"your own personal hoarding...\n"
"<2.so>You're speaking to the right guy, but I'll\n"
"deny I ever told you that.<3.pa> Now let me\n"
"give you a few juicy tidbits about Gorons.\n"
"Those guys eat rock like it's going out of\n"
"style. They just gulp 'em down in one\n"
"swallow! Craziest thing I've ever seen.\n"
"They warm themselves up by taking dips\n"
"in bubbling lava. But where do they get\n"
"the lava? That's the real mystery.\n"
"And most unbelievable of all...<4.pa>\n"
"Gorons don't see any value in gems!\n"
"I had to fan myself awake at hearing that.\n"
"<5.so>Maybe a well-traveled adventurer such\n"
"as yourself knew these things already,\n"
"but I guess now you know them twice."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "MSG_Kyu_01_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Gorons gulp down rock by the mouthful,\n"
"relax in bubbling lava, and don't see any\n"
"value in gems.\n"
"You didn't hear this from me, but...<2.pa>\n"
"that's just plain crazy."
msgstr ""

