msgctxt "MSG_Kyu_04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hey, pal.<2.pa> You're lookin' for info, right?\n"
"<3.so>I got the hottest info around. Rumors,\n"
"fresh off the mill!\n"
"You didn't hear it from me, but they say\n"
"you can float certain ingredients down\n"
"rivers and the fish will come right to you.\n"
"Try a <4.te_si><5.pa>stamella shroom<6.te_si>, and "
"<7.te_si><8.pa>staminoka bass<9.te_si> will\n"
"come chompin'. And if you float a \n"
"<10.te_si><11.pa>hearty truffle<12.te_si>, a <13.te_si><14.pa>hearty "
"bass<15.te_si> will show up.\n"
"Huh? Why am I whispering some things\n"
"and then saying the pertinent information\n"
"at a normal speaking volume?\n"
"<16.so>Listen, pal, just pay attention to the\n"
"name of the ingredient. That seems to be\n"
"an indication of the fish that'll show up."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "MSG_Kyu_04_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Floating certain ingredients down rivers\n"
"will get fish to come right to you.\n"
"\n"
"Send along a stamella shroom to lure a\n"
"staminoka bass or a hearty truffle for a\n"
"hearty bass.\n"
"Apparently the name of the ingredient\n"
"is a hint as to what sort of fish will show\n"
"up. But you didn't hear it from me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Near00"
msgid "The rumor mill churns."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Near01"
msgid "Now that's a nice morsel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Near02"
msgid "A little bird told me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Near03"
msgid "Ahhh, I just love rumors."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Near04"
msgid "I'll start my own rumor."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Rest_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>When I was a child, I heard a rumor that\n"
"shooting stars sometimes fall to Hyrule.<2.pa>\n"
"I like to believe that one's true..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Rest_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I don't get many new scoops when it's\n"
"raining like this.<2.pa> People stay indoors, so\n"
"the rumor mill stops churning."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Rest_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>There's that rumor that lightning will\n"
"strike metal objects.<2.pa> Don't ask how I\n"
"know, but that one is verified as true!"
msgstr ""

