msgctxt "RetMSG_Kyu_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hey, pal. Buddy. <2.pa>Psst...<3.pa> Over here.\n"
"I'm in a talkin' mood, ya see. I've got\n"
"rumors burnin' a hole in my pocket.\n"
"These enemies called \"whales of the\n"
"desert\"—you heard'a them? They're\n"
"blind, but they react to sound.\n"
"If anyone asks, I'll deny giving you this\n"
"info, but if you cut the grass in <4.se_co>Hateno\n"
"Village<5.re_co>, you'll get Hylian rice.\n"
"I've got rumors for days, buddy. They\n"
"say that a <6.se_co>Hinox<7.re_co>'s weak point is its eye.\n"
"\n"
"<8.so>I haven't verified any of this, mind you.\n"
"I'm just a humble rumormonger. I hear a\n"
"thing, say a thing—that's how this works."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: sound
msgctxt "RetMSG_Kyu_01_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>According to the latest rumors, these\n"
"\"whales of the desert\" are blind, but\n"
"they'll react to sound.\n"
"I also heard that if you cut the grass in\n"
"<2.se_co>Hateno Village<3.re_co>, you'll get Hylian rice.\n"
"But you didn't hear that one from me.\n"
"And then there's the one about the\n"
"<4.se_co>Hinox<5.re_co>'s weak point. You know, how it's\n"
"that big ol' eye it loves looking through.\n"
"<6.so>Anyway, whether or not you trust this\n"
"info is up to you. Like I said, I haven't\n"
"verified any of it, so it's your call."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
