#. 6: reset_colour
#. 7: set_colour (blue)
#. 8: reset_colour
msgctxt "RetMSG_Kyu_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You want the latest scoop, don't ya?\n"
"<2.so>I can tell just by lookin' at you, it's all\n"
"over your face. It's in the way you walk!\n"
"Well, the latest talk on the wire is that\n"
"there's a lot of ore to be found in\n"
"<3.se_co>Ludfo's Bog<4.re_co>, over in <5.se_co>Thundra Plateau<6.re_co>."
"\n"
"But just from the name <7.se_co>Thundra Plateau<8.re_co>,\n"
"you can tell that's a dangerous place.\n"
"Don't need a rumor to know that much."
msgstr ""

