#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: set_colour (blue)
#. 7: reset_colour
msgctxt "RetMSG_Kyu_02_1"
msgid ""
"<1.se_co><2.so><3.re_co>The latest talk is that there's a lot of ore\n"
"to be found in <4.se_co>Ludfo's Bog<5.re_co>, over in\n"
"<6.se_co>Thundra Plateau<7.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
msgctxt "RetMSG_Kyu_03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You have the look of a discerning\n"
"individual who loves some juicy info.\n"
"What do you think of this little morsel?\n"
"I heard that giant rock monsters often\n"
"have some good ore just sitting in their\n"
"stomachs. I haven't verified this myself.\n"
"<2.so>But if you try to verify it and wind up\n"
"swallowed whole by one of those things,\n"
"don't come crying to me."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "RetMSG_Kyu_03_1"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I heard that giant rock monsters often\n"
"have some good ore just sitting in their\n"
"stomachs. I haven't verified this myself."
msgstr ""

