msgid ""
"<1.se_co><2.so><3.re_co>Apparently there's some temple-like\n"
"structure at the bottom of <4.se_co>Tanagar\n"
"Canyon<5.re_co>. Might just be a rumor...<6.pa> Or not."
msgstr ""

