#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "SavedLv1_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Phew.<2.pa> Thanks for the assist there, buddy.\n"
"I'll spread rumors of your helpfulness."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "SavedLv1_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Guess I'm OK now. Not that I've verified\n"
"that info for myself..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "SavedLv2_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Thanks, pal.<2.pa> For a moment there I was\n"
"sure I was done for.<3.pa> Maybe this will\n"
"start rumors that I've died."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "SavedLv2_01"
msgid "<1.so>Giving me the cold sweats..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "SavedLv3_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm not so great on a horse, so I was\n"
"having trouble getting away. Thanks for\n"
"coming to help."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "SavedLv3_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Some of these monsters are pretty scary,\n"
"but I guess you're a bit scarier to be able\n"
"to take 'em out like you did."
msgstr ""

